    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个被污染窒息的世界里，居民们如同被催眠般陷入机械化的日常。一位因神秘太阳风暴而蜕变的商人，决定去探索自己所处的这座城市。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/e980b34f8b871aa3166f26b797758842.apng?t=1772105866\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/e980b34f8b871aa3166f26b797758842.poster.avif?t=1772105866\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找一份&quot;真正的&quot;工作，赚取金币……<br>或者……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/06418ab59a7a1e0055f9571ca45f2984.poster.avif?t=1772105866\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/06418ab59a7a1e0055f9571ca45f2984.webm?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/06418ab59a7a1e0055f9571ca45f2984.mp4?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>将居民从数字迷梦中解放出来，为他们灰暗的生活重新涂上色彩。<br>这一切都不用武器……<br>而是靠一把喷壶、一把雨伞……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/cd3173560cf188f60df9ce1034ca593c.poster.avif?t=1772105866\" width=616 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/cd3173560cf188f60df9ce1034ca593c.webm?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/cd3173560cf188f60df9ce1034ca593c.mp4?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以及最重要的：一台收音机录音机。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/ee04613632a267f965a1fbab6e076b5a.poster.avif?t=1772105866\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/ee04613632a267f965a1fbab6e076b5a.webm?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102250/extras/ee04613632a267f965a1fbab6e076b5a.mp4?t=1772105866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>录制、调整声音，然后将它们播放出去，与世界互动。<br>不同的频率会生成不同颜色的光球：有的能唤醒居民，有的能改变环境。<br>你需要做的，就是找到正确的频率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款灵感源自80/90年代经典2D平台的游戏，全手绘制作。<br>融合了动作、冒险和可选的互动对话，并带有讽刺与另类的幽默。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>KOVOCLAK</strong> 对我们这个过度连接、追求效率的社会，投以欢乐而尖锐的一瞥，同时也激发玩家的创造力。<br>准备好用&quot;噪音&quot;来解放这座城市吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
